{"tid":1180582,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【雪姑七友】《心跳500天》導演馬克韋伯 獲斟拍《白雪公主》真人版","createTime":"2019-06-01T02:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T01:12:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6f71d6a5dd3f0cfe9157359f8d7469295a830687","tid":1180582,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:55:57.000Z","msg":"迪士尼近年積極將動畫真人化，單單是今年就已經有《小飛象》（Dumbo）、《阿拉丁》（Aladdin）、《獅子王》（The Lion King）及《黑魔后2》（Maleficent: Mistress of Evil）。而最近有報道指，下一部的真人化計劃就是經典作品《白雪公主》（Snow White），更打算由《心跳500天》（500 Days of Summer）的導演馬克韋伯（Marc Webb）執導。除此之外，《列車上的女孩》（The Girl on the Train）編劇Erin Cressida Wilson將會執筆寫劇本，《星聲夢裡人》（La La Land）的奧斯卡得主Justin Paul與Benj Pasek則會為電影寫歌。<br />\n其實今次已非第一次《白雪公主》的故事真人化，之前茱莉亞羅拔絲（Julia Roberts）與莉莉歌連絲（Lily Collins）主演的《魔鏡．魔鏡：白雪公主決戰黑心皇后》（Mirror Mirror），已經是將此經典故事改編成電影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190531/large/1559299141_a25d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190531%2Flarge%2F1559299141_a25d.jpg&h=f8871af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190601/59662957\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190601%2F59662957&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=de6a95d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190601%2F59662957&h=c3c6664a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190601/59662957</a>"},{"pid":"0c449fea2f0b5f2a51f7867ca5119d30f7641634","tid":1180582,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e19ff606213dc56b2d1bfe1a7498a12e017837c1","tid":1180582,"uid":245813,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:49:07.000Z","ms